#

Lemon Basil Grilled Salmon with Asparagus

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleoHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

GrilledHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A refreshing and healthy grilled salmon dish with vibrant lemon and fresh basil, paired with tender asparagus.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • asparagus spears: 1 bunch (about 1 lb)
